{
  "stem": "2226.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they-- they were-- they were so good, nobody could-- how I know it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because I had two boys from mine city, only still alive in New York.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were named Biermann.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were watchmakers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they made it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In the meantime, when I come to Sachsenhausen, I finally found out that our transport from Auschwitz, from [INAUDIBLE] over there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Oh where-- so he comes over there, and he calls it-- when you come?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When you come?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Anybody from Ciechanow?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I say, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] [LAUGHS] That was that neighbor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We were brought up together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And not Semetic bigots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Couldn't be a bigot in the camp we was going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So in the meantime, when I came over there, they wanted to take away my shoes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They wanted-- and my clothes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, but they were so good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So he stayed with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he went over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He was an old fellow, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He said, listen, don't you touch that [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- and from over there, it was the few days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I said, oh, the whole [NON-ENGLISH], right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "The whole-- I mean, factory, where I used to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The-- the Polacks, they brought him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They brought him to Sachsenhausen too, like to work in the [NON-ENGLISH] factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I don't know that it was over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But they make airplanes-- Messerschmitt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I don't if you ever hear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Say it again, please?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Messerschmitt.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was a few days over there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, they took us to Kaufering.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then-- that was before, on-- before Christmas-- on Christmas time-- took us to Kaufering and Lage Rhine.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went to [INAUDIBLE] over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From over there, they took us to-- to Lage Leven.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was with a girl tehre.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She-- she-- she don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, it used to be Raditsky family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She didn't-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
